{"tid":1550353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"立場哥哥，多謝你","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:02:42.000Z","uid":301132,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"856c21019f0ed7cf0253f3f9e4ce783dd2ab9e45","tid":1550353,"uid":301132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:40:53.000Z","msg":"睇住立場live，沙田閘內。<br />\n望住黑警趕記者走，立場哥哥好堅持唔肯走，不停重覆唔可以再次發生831太子站事件，記者唔會走。<br />\n<br />\n果下真係好想喊，好多謝一班記者。<br />\n義士不是condom！香港人唔會忘記你地！<br />\n太子站真相未還原！交CCTV！"},{"pid":"7854553dd984bceab506a2aaaef67944d525b62b","tid":1550353,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:41:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68a592d3c1b310d6f417b1c97e8000e95ea77783","tid":1550353,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a73b3867005b4e3528730550d31776e59c0ececb","tid":1550353,"uid":46966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />昇哥好野 <br />\n